Ahmed Ololade (amụrụ na 13 Jenụwarị 1995), nke a maara dịka Asake, bu onye n’agụ egwu ya na onye na ede egwu Afrobeats nke Naijiria. Ọ bịanyere aka na YBNL Nation na Empire Distribution. Aha egwu ya na-asọpụrụ nne ya, onye aha mbụ ya bụ Asake.
Asake gụrụ ihe nkiri na nka na Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo, Ile-Ife, Osun steeti
Ọ bụ ezie na, ọ nọ na-ewepụta egwu kemgbe 2018, ọrụ egwu ya gara n'ihu na 2020 mgbe ọ wepụtara egwu "Mr
Money". A remix na Zlatan na Peruzzi sochiri
Ọ malitere na ụlọ ọrụ ahụ mgbe ọ kwụsịrị egwu 2020, Lady
Ọ ghọrọ onye ama ama mgbe onye isi ụlọ ọrụ, Olamide bịanyere aka na YBNL Records na Febụwarị 2022.
N'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2022, Asake wepụtara egwu izizi ya bụ Ololade, nke gosipụtara egwu egwu Asake bụ "Omo Ope” nkeOlamide so ya wee guọ
Otu egwu ọzọ a tọhapụrụ n'egwuregwu ahụ ga-abụ nke a na-emegharị otu ọnwa ka e mesịrị na amaokwu sitere n'aka onye na-ese ihe na Naijiria bụ Burna Boy
Asake emesịri bịanye aka na nkwekọrịta nkesa na Empire na July 2022.
Asake wepụtara abọm studio mbụ ya Mr
Money With the Vibe na Septemba 8, 2022, ọnwa asaa mgbe a tọhapụrụ EP mbụ ya
Abọm ahụ nwetara nkwado site na egwu egwu, "Terminator", "Peace Be Unto You" na "Sungba" remix na Burna Boy

Abọm ahụ nwetara otuto dị elu site n'aka ndị na-akwado ya na mba ya nke Naịjirịa, yana n'ofe ụwa wee gaa n'ihu na-agbaji ọtụtụ ndekọ n'ụwa niile. Ọ gakwara n'ihu ịhazi njem zuru ụwa ọnụ maka abọm izizi ya, na-aga n'ihu ire O2 Academy Brixton na Obodo ndi ocha. N'abalị iri abụọ na otu n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 2022, Roqqu, kpughere Asake dị ka onye nnọchi anya ha kachasị ọhụrụ.
Asake na-ejikarị mmepụta Afro na Amapiano eme ihe. E nwere akụkụ nke Fújì n'abụ ya.
